CatDescriptText: A headline of a newspaper on a desk reads, ". . .Blasted for Hastie Maneuver, NAACP Board Fights For Harmony".
TitMainTitle: Women staff in Pittsburgh Courier office, including Ida Mae Mauney, Frances Nunn, Myrtle Lewis, Revella Tunie, Bea Williams, Ms. Robinson, Elizabeth Barrow, and Betty Stokes with Philip Morris bellhop Johnny Roventini, posed in PIttsburgh Courier offices, another version
